Member's Rights and How to Exercise Them
Your other rights.
You also have the right to objectively explain how we correct, delete, use, and share your data, and to restrict how we use or share your data. We will respond to all requests within a reasonable time after receiving them. If you have a privacy or data use concern that has not been resolved to your satisfaction, you may contact the Korea Consumer Affairs Organization (free of charge) in the country where we are located.
• Flyff Legacy Customer Service -
https://galalab.helpshift.com/hc/ko/4-flyff-legacy/
How We Protect Your Data
In processing your personal information, we take the following technical and administrative measures to ensure the safety of your personal information so that it is not lost, stolen, leaked, altered, or damaged.
•
Members' personal information is stored encrypted, and when it is necessary to transmit such personal information, it is transmitted securely using encrypted communication.
•
We back up and manage important data from time to time to prevent damage to personal information, and install and operate regularly updated antivirus programs to prevent infection with malware or viruses.
•
We minimize the number of people in charge of handling personal information, and conduct regular or ongoing training and campaigns for personal information handlers and company-wide employees.
Rights of Members and Legal Representatives and How to Exercise Them
In principle, the Company destroys the information after the purpose of collecting and using personal information is fulfilled. However, if it is necessary to preserve it in accordance with the provisions of the relevant laws and regulations, the Company will keep the member's information for a certain period of time stipulated by the relevant laws and regulations.
Members and their legal representatives may request the deletion of their personal information or that of their children under the age of 14 at any time, and the Company will take necessary measures without delay upon such request.
To delete personal information of a member or child under the age of 14, please contact our customer service, and after going through the identification procedure, you can delete and withdraw.
• Flyff Legacy Customer Service https://galalab.helpshift.com/hc/ko/4-flyff-legacy/
We will process personal information deleted at the request of a member or legal representative as specified in the 'Personal Information Retention and Use Period' and will not be able to view or use it for any other purpose.
