Introduction
If you reside outside of the Republic of Korea, the terms of this agreement (the "Terms of Service") govern the relationship between you and GALA LAB CORP. and/or its affiliates ( "GALA LAB CORP." "we," or "us") regarding your play or use of, or participation in, GALA LAB CORP. mobile games ("Games") and related services and game support applications, including, without limitation,
Every GALA LAB CORP. App or other game related applications ("Application” or "Applications”), GALA LAB CORP. branded websites (“Websites”), online communities for Games or social network services offered platform for Games (collectively, the "Services").
Use of the Services is also governed by the privacy policy of GALA LAB CORP. (“Privacy Policy”) as well as the GALA LAB CORP.'s community standards, which are incorporated herein by reference. We may collect and use your content and information in accordance with the Privacy Policy.
By downloading or playing the Game, accessing and/or using the Services, and/or creating a GALA LAB CORP. account, you accept and agree to be bound by the Terms of Service, the Privacy Policy, and the GALA LAB CORP.'s community standards (collectively, the "GALA LAB CORP. Policy”). By agreeing with the GALA LAB CORP. Policy, You represent that you are not a person barred from receiving services under the laws of applicable jurisdictions. You also represent that you are thirteen (13) years of age or older If you are between the ages of 13 and 18, you represent that
your legal guardian has reviewed and agrees to the Terms of Service.
GALA LAB CORP. may amend, at its discretion, any portion of the GALA LAB CORP. Policy at any time by posting or displaying the amended GALA LAB CORP. Policy within and/or on the Games, or any of the Websites. You will be deemed to have accepted such amendments by continuing to use the Service. Except as otherwise stated, any such amendments will be automatically effective after they are initially posted.
