Dormant Characters
Item Contents
In order to prevent a member's character from being used for unappropriate purposes and to ensure smoother game services, GALA LAB Corp. may classify the character as a dormant character and oragnize and store related information separate from the server if all of the following requirements are met.
1. Characters which have no history of accessing the game for more than 12 months
2. Characters from 1. of which does not have any paid items with a remaining usage period.
